    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "those are good starting points, but they're a bit generic for a high-level debate. can you flesh them out more? specifically, could you expand on the economic arguments and the national security aspect? my students need the kind of nuanced, high-level reasoning that opponents would actually bring up in a round, not just the basics.",
